Products | Surna







































































Phone: 303.993.5271  |  OTCQB: SRNA 







































Products 










Efficient, Reliable, Intelligent





Menu








Efficient. Reliable.  Intelligent. It’s not just our tagline, it’s what we strive to achieve with every product we sell. At Surna, our products go through vigorous testing to ensure they meet our standards before they are ever released to the public. Designed specifically with the indoor garden in mind, our products will deliver the results you are looking for.





Efficient
Our products are designed to work more efficiently for your grow. After all, the less you have to worry about the products you are using, the more time to you have to dedicate to perfecting your growing technique.





Reliable
Consistency and reliability are key to a functional growing environment. Our products are designed with the knowledge that your grow runs all day, every day and the equipment you use needs to be able to keep up.





Intelligent
We see a need for intelligent solutions for your garden. Every product we make is designed to make things easier and better for you. From our very first product, water-chilled climate control systems, to our current developments, we are working to find a better way.








Our ultimate goal is to be a one-stop shop for all your indoor garden and greenhouse needs. We are working hard to bring new and innovative technology to the garden.
If you don’t see exactly what you want, contact us at 303.993.5271 and we can work with you to develop what you need.








Climate Control Products
Climate control plays a large part in the quality of product produced. With the proper climate control system, you can maximize productivity, quality and volume while simultaneously minimizing monthly expenses. To do this, you need a system that has been designed to meet the needs of indoor gardens.
 


				Learn More							














Surna Reflector


We’ve redesigned every aspect of the standard grow reflector to better fit growers’ exact needs.

													View Product →












Commercial Chillers


Specifically designed for large commercial garden environments, Surna chillers provide top-of-the-line cooling power.

													View Product →












Fan Coils


Ductless air handlers create a sealed indoor garden to maintain climate and prevent pest introduction.

													View Product →












Dehumidifiers


Surna’s commercial-grade Dehumidifier is ideal for the unique indoor garden environment.

													View Product →











Biosecurity Products
Biosecurity refers to the measures taken to reduce the likelihood of harmful organisms being introduced to or spread throughout a cultivation facility. Just like with any other form of security, there are various levels of biosecurity, ranging from basic, critical steps, to the more involved steps that are implemented when it is of the utmost importance to minimize risks to the highest extent possible.
 


				Learn More							














Air Sanitation


Photocatalytic reaction provides sanitized air and minimizes breakouts of pests, pathogens and mold.

													View Product →












